	Armani Foxed    
	 London, Jan. 13: Megan Fox has been announced as the new face of Emporio Armani, reports The Daily Telegraph.      
	The actress, who stars in the Transformers films, will front Armanis spring/summer campaigns this year, with photographs of the 23-year-old modelling the designer underwear set to appear on billboards in cities across the world.       
	Promotional shots released on Wednesday show the brunette posing in underwear, mini skirts and tight shirts.
                                                                                                                                                      
